# Build outputs
bin/
obj/
dist/
dist-*/
package-smoke/
packaging/staging/
packaging/RecognitionSmokeOut/
packaging/setup-previews/
packaging/SnapAnchor.Setup/bin/
packaging/SnapAnchor.Setup/obj/
packaging/SnapAnchor.Setup/Payload.zip
